
Specifications:

- Backend: Ruby On Rails

Ruby 2.4, Rails 5.1
ActiveRecord with Sqlite
Devise and Devise-Auth-Token for Authentication
Pundit for Authorization
Kaminari for Pagination
Faker for Data Seeder
Serializer for formatted data


- front end:

ReactJS 15
Redux, Redux-Thunk, Redux-Form
Redux-Await for tracking status of async actions
Create-React-App for bootstrapping
Material UI for layouts and components
Recompose for enhancing functional components
Lodash for array, object operations
Axios for API Interaction
AirBnb ESLint for beautiful coding
